      "description": "Product Description: Elevate your laptop charging experience with the Dell 65W Laptop Charger ! This charger is purpose-built for Dell Inspiron 1546, XPS M1330, M1530 Series laptops , delivering high-performance power to keep your device ready to conquer your day, whether at work or play. Key Features: 65W Output : Delivers swift and efficient charging to keep your laptop powered up for both work and entertainment. Wide Compatibility : Seamlessly fits a range of Dell Inspiron 1546, XPS M1330, M1530 Series laptops, making it versatile for users with different models. Steady Power : Provides a 19.5V output with a 3.34A current rating for dependable, consistent power flow. User-Friendly Design : Featuring an easy-to-use 7.4*5.0MM pin connector, the charger eliminates the hassle of tangled cords and ensures a simple, reliable connection. Never let a low battery slow you down again. Invest in the Dell 65W Laptop Charger – a reliable, energy-efficient, and performance-driven solution. It’s your passport to staying connected and powered up wherever life takes you. Upgrade your laptop’s charging capabilities today, and experience the difference a high-quality charger can make. Order now, and never worry about running out of power again! Make the Dell 65W Laptop Charger your choice for uninterrupted performance. Don’t wait; stay charged – order yours today! | Compatible Battery Part Numbers: Battery part number / SKU: 65w 7.4mm | Compatible Laptop Models: Series Models Dell Inspiron Series 1110, 1120, 1121, 1122, 1150, 11z, 13, 1318, 1370, 14, 1410, 1420, 1427, 1440, 1464, 1470, 14z, 15, 1501, 1520, 1521, 1525, 1526, 1545, 1564, 1570, 15z, 1750, 1764, 17R, 300M, 3137, 3420, 3421, 3520, 3521, 3537, 3721, 3737, 400, 500M, 505M, 510M, 5323, 5420, 5421, 5423, 5437, 5520, 5521, 5537, 5720, 5721, 5737, 6000, 600MD, 610MD, 630MD, 6400, 640MD, 660s, 700M, 710M, 7720 Dell XPS Series M1330, M1530, M1210, M140, XPSM140 Dell Latitude Series 100L, 131L, 2100, 2110, 