      "featured": false,
      "description": "Ant Esports 690 Air Mid Tower ARGB Gaming Cabinet Multiple Radiator Mounts – For enthusiast-grade cooling dual 360-millimeter radiators are supported on the top and front panel while a single 240mm is supported on the side to keep the most extreme systems cool. Large Storage Options – Dual 2.5” SSD mounts and dual 3.5” HDD mounts the Ant Esports 690 Air is ideal to build any gaming or production system. Movable Disk Bracket – The HDD cage under the PSU shroud is movable and can be slid towards the front to make space for long PSUs and increase it to 220mm if needed. Spacious Interiors – The spacious interior fits upto an E-ATX motherboard configuration. Support for up to a 390mm graphics card, a 175mm CPU cooler, and up to a 220mm PSU in length provides room for upgrades. Four Dust Filters – With magnetic dust filters in the front, side, and top along with a pull tray one on the PSU, the 690 Air facilitates high airflow while filtering out dust particles. | Compatible Battery Part Numbers: Battery part number / SKU: Ant Esports 690 Air Mid | Compatible Laptop Models: Model family reference: Ant Esports 690 Air Mid Tower ARGB Gaming Cabinet | Please match part number and laptop model before purchase.\n\nCompatible Battery Part Numbers: Battery part number / SKU: Ant Esports 690 Air Mid\n\nCompatible Laptop Models: Model family reference: Ant Esports 690 Air Mid Tower ARGB Gaming Cabinet",
