      "fulfillment": "fbm",
      "featured": false,
      "description": "Ant Esports 510 Air Mid Tower ARGB Gaming Cabinet High Air Flow – With a tapered mesh design in the front the 510 Air delivers high airflow to keep even the most demanding systems cool under extreme conditions. Four ARGB Fans – The Ant Esports 510 Flow comes with four high CFM 120mm ARGB fans pre-installed that can be controlled via motherboard software like MSI Mystic Lights, Asus Aura, Gigabyte RGB Fusion, etc. Roomy Interior – Support for up to a 360mm long graphics card, a 160mm CPU cooler, and up to an E-ATX motherboard provides room for upgrades to stay ahead of the game. Vertical GPU Mount – The 510 Air supports vertical GPU support right out of the box so you can flaunt your graphics card with ease. Multiple Storage Options – With two dedicated 2.5” SSD mounts and two interchangeable trays supporting either a 3.5” HDD or a 2.5” SSD gives multiple options to mount storage drives in the order of your choice. | Compatible Battery Part Numbers: Battery part number / SKU: Ant Esports 510 Air Mid | Compatible Laptop Models: Model family reference: Ant Esports 510 Air Mid Tower ARGB Gaming Cabinet | Please match part number and laptop model before purchase.\n\nCompatible Battery Part Numbers: Battery part number / SKU: Ant Esports 510 Air Mid\n\nCompatible Laptop Models: Model family reference: Ant Esports 510 Air Mid Tower ARGB Gaming Cabinet",
