      "featured": false,
      "description": "Ant Esports ICE-120AG Mid Tower Gaming Cabinet Premium finish with A-RGB panel : Solid build quality with a metallic finish and an integrated Auto RGB panel in the front makes it the perfect fit for a modern retro build aiming for a monolithic design. Ample of Cooling : Can house up to eight 120mm fans for the optimum cooling experience. Spacious Interiors : Can accommodate large air coolers of up to 160mm height and dual graphics cards up to 265mm in length each. Magnetic Dust Filters : Comes with dual magnetic dust filters, one at the bottom and one on top for a dust-free interior and easy maintenance. Easy Wire Management : Comes with a perforated PSU shroud for proper ventilation as well as easier and cleaner wire management. Fully Loaded IO Panel : The ICE 120 AG is equipped with 1 x USB 2.0, 1 x USB 3.0, 1 x Audio In, 1 x Mic on the front IO panel leaving no room for any complaints whatsoever. Multiple Storage Options : With a dedicated SSD mount and three caddies, the cabinet can either house two SSDs and two HDDs or one HDD and four SSDs. | Compatible Battery Part Numbers: Battery part number / SKU: Ant Esports ICE-200TG | Compatible Laptop Models: Model family reference: Ant Esports ICE-200TG Mid Tower Gaming Cabinet | Please match part number and laptop model before purchase.\n\nCompatible Battery Part Numbers: Battery part number / SKU: Ant Esports ICE-200TG\n\nCompatible Laptop Models: Model family reference: Ant Esports ICE-200TG Mid Tower Gaming Cabinet",
